Application.Domain

Class Answer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.Answer

  • @Entity
public class Answer
extends java.lang.Object
    Answer is the class that maps the database Entity Answer. An Answer is the representation of the answer provided by the User to a Question of a Quiz.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
